Revision history for Perl module Crypt::SHAVS.

0.02  Sat Dec 10 02:34:10 MST 2011
	- Removed dependency on Digest::SHA
	- Added example scripts for checking CPAN SHA modules
	- Renamed various files for greater clarity and conciseness

0.01  Tue Dec  6 06:12:24 MST 2011
	- Original version
		-- regarded as initial prototype
		-- interface might change radically
	- Try using the most familiar output format
		-- based on "check" mode of md5sum/shasum
		-- minus the WARNINGs and summaries
	- Digest::SHA is not actually required for Crypt::SHAVS
		-- but it's currently the easiest way to test it
		-- this PREREQ will certainly change in the future
	- Object-oriented programming interface
		-- two methods only, to emphasize ease of use

